{"tid":2017797,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"兒子長大竟撞臉前隊友　男星哭到發抖驗DNA證實慘戴綠帽16年","createTime":"2020-05-15T09:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T10:06:35.000Z","uid":1121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f05c3df38239198bfd1af69e14fcdfad434cad02","tid":2017797,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.mirrormedia.com.tw/assets/images/20200513111448-678329aada4d1a6e98c95243d47be634-tablet.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.com.tw%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F20200513111448-678329aada4d1a6e98c95243d47be634-tablet.jpg&h=a5fe8c9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大澤樹生（左圖右、右圖）7年前在記者會上泣訴兒子大澤零次（左圖左）並非自己親生骨肉。（翻攝自日本雅虎）<br />\n<br />\n日本傑尼斯男團「光源氏」在80年代紅極一時，是家喻戶曉的偶像團體，成員大澤樹生退團隔年和女星喜嶋多舞奉子成婚，未料9年後因個性不合離婚，而最戲劇化的莫過於大澤樹生在2013年當眾泣訴養了16年的兒子大澤零次並非親生，眼尖網友也發現大澤零次與他昔日隊友赤坂晃有父子臉，相似度高達9成。"},{"pid":"08313969e0f760334507a543018f462e75f967ae","tid":2017797,"uid":1121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:14:31.000Z","msg":"大澤樹生與喜多嶋舞在1996年奉子結婚、2005年離婚，兩人離婚後兒子大澤零次的撫養權雖歸給喜多嶋舞，但大澤零次卻和大澤樹生同住。沒想到大澤零次長大後和「爸爸」大澤樹生愈來愈不像，讓大澤樹生起了疑心，懷疑兒子和他並無血緣關係。他驗了DNA後發現，大澤零次真的不是自己親生骨肉，綠光罩頂幫別人養了16年的兒子，被週刊爆料後，神隱一個月後才召開記者會說明事件始末。2013年大澤樹生在記者會上聲淚俱下證實這個驚人事實，哭到發抖，連一句話都說不完整，畫面令人同情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mirrormedia.com.tw/assets/images/20200513111500-a0193da065d6a13ce6bf556558787ca1-tablet.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.com.tw%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F20200513111500-a0193da065d6a13ce6bf556558787ca1-tablet.jpg&h=dd81464a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友發現大澤零次（右）與赤坂晃（左）長得愈來愈像，直指兩人有父子臉。（翻攝自日本雅虎）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，淡出演藝圈多年的前妻喜多嶋舞，在2015年接受媒體訪問時，堅持大澤零次的親生父親就是大澤樹生，更透露大澤樹生是她的初戀，懷疑是親子鑑定結果出錯，希望能再驗一次還她清白。而去年大澤零次爆出毆打女友醜聞被捕後，大澤樹生的綠帽事件再次引發關注。有網友直指大澤零次撞臉「光源氏」另一成員赤坂晃，讓大澤零次身世之謎再成網友茶餘飯後的話題。"},{"pid":"60414fa3d384829107c8505ef38981ab2bc6bd33","tid":2017797,"uid":309553,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:15:46.000Z","msg":"lucas<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8237edeca0f7cccc7fbfecb737b96e07c14a6be1","tid":2017797,"uid":3358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:15:48.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，呢單野斬撚死個前隊友我都唔覺得過份"},{"pid":"5f634bd27fab6bcd596ddc40a9c41e9d3c1edc06","tid":2017797,"uid":68689,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2020/05/15/423639/i_640x949_074017496.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2020%2F05%2F15%2F423639%2Fi_640x949_074017496.jpg&h=837e5251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8dd7aa09e44f7c11c7f4932c22a153898f6264","tid":2017797,"uid":37912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:20:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"177e197467205de93c0d98a6309553aae2cd09fd","tid":2017797,"uid":36995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f634bd27fab6bcd596ddc40a9c41e9d3c1edc06","tid":2017797,"uid":68689,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2020/05/15/423639/i_640x949_074017496.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2020%2F05%2F15%2F423639%2Fi_640x949_074017496.jpg&h=837e5251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"3兄弟<br />\n3個姓<br />\n陳，謝，White"},{"pid":"5c3a4b756e3d4f6e1c2a6ed1344c839ab8b366f3","tid":2017797,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> SOD 原來是真的"},{"pid":"6b8f92874a0761493bf3e4b5a0bc17c1db847868","tid":2017797,"uid":242444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:06:35.000Z","msg":"日本妹世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}